flowchart TD
    A[Teacher logs in] --> B[Dashboard]
    B --> C[Select Subject & Enter Student Marks]
    C --> D[System evaluates performance]
    D --> E{Marks >= Pass Threshold?}
    E -->|Yes| F[Save Record & Update Dashboard]
    E -->|No| G[Save Record & Trigger Email Alert]
    G --> H[Send Email Notification to Parent/Guardian]
    H --> I[Log Notification Event]
    F --> J[Process Completed]
    I --> J
